'''歐卡'''（Henry Okah，{{bd|1965年|||}}），是[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]游擊隊[[尼日爾三角洲解放運動|尼日爾三角洲解放運動]]的領導人。尼日爾三角洲運營的石油公司受襲，尼日爾三角洲解放運動承認責任。該運動襲擊形式常包括破壞、[[游擊戰|游擊戰]]或者綁架外國石油公司工人。叛軍的目的是破壞外國在[[尼日爾三角洲|尼日爾三角洲]]的[[石油|石油]]利益。他們指這些外國公司剝削本土民眾。

歐卡于2008年2月在安哥拉被捕并被引渡到尼日利亚，他被指控犯叛国罪、恐怖主义罪、非法持有枪支和武器贩运罪等62項罪名<ref name=voa>{{cite news|first=Gilbert |last=da Costa |title=Suspected Nigerian Militant Faces More Charges at Secret Trial |url=http://voanews.com/english/2008-07-07-voa21.cfm?renderforprint=1&textonly=1&&CFID=10617603&CFTOKEN=67027532 |work=[[Voice_of_America_News|Voice of America News]] |date=2008-07-28 |accessdate=2013-10-16 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080709082530/http://voanews.com/english/2008-07-07-voa21.cfm?renderforprint=1&textonly=1&&CFID=10617603&CFTOKEN=67027532 |archive-date=July 9, 2008 }}</ref>。由於尼日爾三角洲解放運動表示如果歐卡被釋放，他們願意放下武器。於是2009年7月13日，歐卡被釋放<ref name="Nigeria releases key rebel leader">{{cite news | title = Nigeria releases key rebel leader | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8148535.stm | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | date = 2009-07-13 | accessdate = 2009-07-13 | archive-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210801155320/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8148535.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2013年1月21日，南非法院判定歐卡犯下13项恐怖主义罪行指控，其中包括2010年10月1日在[[阿布贾|阿布贾]]造成12人死亡的爆炸事件<ref name="South African Court Convicts Henry Okah">{{cite news | title = Breaking news: S/Africa court convicts Henry Okah of 13 acts of terrorism | url = http://www.vanguardngr.com/2013/01/breaking-news-safrica-court-convicts-henry-okah-of-13-acts-of-terrorism/ | publisher = [[Vanguard_Nigeria|Vanguard Nigeria]] | date = 2013-01-21 | accessdate = 2013-01-23 | archive-date = 2018-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180813043945/https://www.vanguardngr.com/2013/01/breaking-news-safrica-court-convicts-henry-okah-of-13-acts-of-terrorism/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。最終歐卡被判24年監禁<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://thestreetjournal.org/2012/05/%E2%80%9Cjonathan-begged-me-to-blame-north-for-october-1-blasts%E2%80%9D-henry-okah-claims/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-01-03 |archive-date=2012-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120506074422/http://thestreetjournal.org/2012/05/%E2%80%9Cjonathan-begged-me-to-blame-north-for-october-1-blasts%E2%80%9D-henry-okah-claims/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年3月7日又被判處終身監禁。

